---
title: Creamy Tex-Mex Pulled Pork Fusilli with Cheddar & Coriander
description: Here’s a cuisine combo we’re excited to try - Mexican and Italian! Pulled pork is cooked in a creamy tomato sauce with Tex-Mex
spices, before being tossed through golden twirls of fusili and Cheddar cheese. This meal is sure to be a hit with the whole family!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66582af4a8b29b0c10df458a-7b6ce8dc.jpeg
